{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhhpi4vtu080","created":1775035311628,"text":"视频号"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhhpic87n2g0","created":1775035327614,"text":"差评处理","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-22.999999314546812,"y":-158.99999526143105}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhhpilwxcco0","created":1775035348699,"text":"12-15/条，底线价格：10/条","priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpplsk2e80","created":1775035896984,"text":"客户问会不会违规：我们最近一直在使用这种方式，没有出现过任何违规的情况！","priority":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpjtw6sog0","created":1775035444433,"text":"切记：只能豁免体验分，内容处理不掉","priority":3},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpjh2wli00","created":1775035416541,"text":"处理方式：更改物流方式","priority":4},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpodfe8ag0","created":1775035800410,"text":"不用补偿","priority":5},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpigli5r40","created":1775035337125,"text":"品退","layout_mind_offset":{"x":333.9999900460249,"y":151.9999954700474}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhhpkddpy1k0","created":1775035486852,"text":"12-15/条，底线价格10/条","layout_right_offset":{"x":393.9999882578854,"y":-18.999999433755818},"priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpq6woe3c0","created":1775035942946,"text":"客户问会不会违规：我们最近一直在使用这种方式，没有出现过任何违规的情况！","layout_right_offset":{"x":678.9999797642237,"y":-23.999999284744433},"priority":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpnrfw0rs0","created":1775035752551,"text":"处理方式：联系客户（商家要是没问就别说，因为这个跟商家说了他们自己也能处理了）","layout_right_offset":{"x":710.9999788105495,"y":-0.9999999701978481},"priority":3},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhpo5lcd680","created":1775035783356,"text":"需要补偿；根据客单价多少，来谈补偿多少，这个补偿的意思是补偿给客户（也就是买东西的人）尽量谈高点","layout_right_offset":{"x":817.9999756217007,"y":9.999999701977003},"priority":4},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}